%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Instead%20of%20hosting%20Thanksgiving%2C%20I%20took%20my%20family%20to%20an%20all-inclusive%20resort%20in%20Mexico.%20It's%20become%20our%20new%20favorite%20tradition.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221518%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20people%20pose%20on%20a%20beach%20holding%20a%20frame%20that%20says%20%26quot%3BGive%20Thanks%2C%20Happy%20Thanksgiving.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6903bdd1599d46a4ccc12c68%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221139%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20spent%20Thanksgiving%20on%20a%20family%20vacation%20to%20an%20all-inclusive%20resort.%3Cp%3ETaima%20Ramsey%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ELast%20year%2C%20my%20family%20traveled%20to%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fall-inclusive-resort-for-adults-atelier-playa-mujeres-review-2025-4%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eall-inclusive%20resort%20in%20Mexico%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20Thanksgiving.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAlthough%20it%20felt%20strange%20to%20stray%20from%20our%20traditions%2C%20we%20had%20an%20incredible%20time.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20fact%2C%20we'll%20be%20spending%20Thanksgiving%20on%20the%20resort%20again%20this%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20I%20had%20a%20wild%20idea%20during%20Easter%20dinner%3A%20%26quot%3BWhat%20if%20we%20skipped%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Forder-thanksgiving-dinner-instead-of-cooking-it-best-deals-benefits%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecooking%20for%20Thanksgiving%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20went%20to%20Mexico%20instead%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20room%20went%20silent%2C%20and%20I%20wasn't%20sure%20if%20that%20was%20good%20or%20bad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20traditional%20Puerto%20Rican%20family%2C%20where%20Thanksgiving%20is%20spent%20at%20home%20with%20family%20and%20friends%2C%20eating%20an%20obscene%20amount%20of%20traditional%20food%20like%20pasteles%20and%20pernil.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20when%20I%20told%20everyone%20I%20wanted%20to%20spend%20Thanksgiving%20at%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fall-inclusive-resort-mistakes-to-avoid-from-frequent-traveler%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eall-inclusive%20resort%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Mexico%2C%20it%20blew%20their%20minds.%20However%2C%20I%20had%20no%20clue%20this%20was%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20new%20family%20tradition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a8145d14-5027-44dc-9701-6ee3d351b466%5C%22%3EChanging%20our%20traditions%20was%20difficult%20but%20worth%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20family%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcelebrating-thanksgiving-early-perks-worth-it-for-family%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecelebrated%20Thanksgiving%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20same%20way%20for%20generations%2C%20so%20suggesting%20we%20do%20something%20different%20was%20bold.%20It%20meant%20breaking%20a%20decades-long%20tradition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20preparing%20a%20whole%20meal%20%E2%80%94%20and%20sometimes%20a%20whole%20weekend%20of%20meals%20%E2%80%94%20for%20a%20family%20that%20seems%20to%20grow%20every%20year%20has%20become%20exhausting.%20The%20idea%20of%20no%20cooking%20and%20cleaning%20for%20a%20week%20sounded%20amazing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20wasn't%20easy.%20We%20knew%20not%20everyone%20would%20be%20able%20to%20join%20us%2C%20and%20we%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20enjoy%20some%20of%20our%20favorite%20holiday%20dishes%2C%20which%20we%20look%20forward%20to%20each%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20promise%20of%20lazy%20days%20sipping%20margaritas%20on%20the%20beach%2C%20all-you-can-eat%20food%2C%20and%20not%20having%20to%20lift%20a%20finger%20was%20too%20good%20to%20pass%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20everyone%20was%20convinced%2C%20tickets%20were%20booked%2C%20bags%20were%20packed%2C%20and%20we%20all%20arrived%20safely%20(and%20on%20time)%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmargaritaville-island-reserve-riviera-maya-cancun-mexico-worth-it-review-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eresort%20in%20Riviera%20Maya%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20day%20before%20Thanksgiving.%20There%20were%2016%20of%20us%2C%20ranging%20in%20age%20from%20my%207-year-old%20niece%20to%20my%2070-year-old%20uncle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223017%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20all-inclusive%20resort%20with%20pools%2C%20fountains%2C%20and%20palm%20trees.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69091671c007ca8c27382683%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222065%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20Thanksgiving%20celebration%20looked%20a%20little%20different%2C%20but%20it%20was%20just%20as%20meaningful.%3Cp%3ETaima%20Ramsey%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20spent%20the%20day%20sipping%20cold%20drinks%20by%20the%20pool%2C%20napping%20after%20early%20flights%2C%20and%20talking%20excitedly%20about%20our%20plans%20for%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20actual%20holiday%2C%20we%20played%20games%20on%20the%20beach%2C%20swam%20in%20the%20warm%20sea%2C%20ate%20fresh%20tacos%2C%20and%20joined%20a%20pool%20party%20in%20the%20afternoon.%20It%20didn't%20feel%20like%20Thanksgiving%2C%20since%20the%20day%20is%20usually%20spent%20in%20the%20kitchen%20trying%20to%20prepare%20everything%20for%20the%20big%20evening%20meal%20%E2%80%94%20but%20that%20was%20part%20of%20the%20magic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20we%20spend%20time%20together%20at%20home%20during%20the%20holidays%2C%20laughing%2C%20eating%2C%20and%20singing%20karaoke%20until%20midnight.%20But%20someone%20always%20has%20to%20cook%2C%20clean%2C%20and%20keep%20things%20going.%20Not%20having%20to%20worry%20about%20that%20gave%20us%20the%20freedom%20to%20just%20have%20a%20good%20time%20and%20really%20enjoy%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20one%20of%20the%20hardest%20things%20about%20stepping%20away%20from%20tradition%20is%20giving%20up%20the%20comfort%20of%20familiar%20foods%20and%20customs.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20turkey%20or%20pernil%2C%20and%20instead%2C%20we%20had%20dinner%20at%20the%20resort's%20fusion%20restaurant.%20I%20got%20a%20lobster%20risotto%2C%20my%20husband%20had%20filet%20mignon%2C%20and%20my%20parents%20chose%20the%20catch%20of%20the%20day.%20We%20had%20everything%20except%20turkey%2C%20and%20that%20was%20OK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20it%20felt%20just%20like%20any%20other%20Thanksgiving.%20We%20laughed%2C%20we%20joked%2C%20and%20we%20shared%20stories%20as%20if%20we%20were%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20was%20hard%20celebrating%20without%20some%20of%20my%20favorite%20cousins%2C%20I%20made%20sure%20to%20FaceTime%20them%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20even%20able%20to%20put%20a%20new%20spin%20on%20one%20of%20our%20favorite%20traditions%20%E2%80%94%20dancing%20after%20dinner%20to%20burn%20off%20calories.%20But%20this%20time%2C%20instead%20of%20dancing%20in%20la%20sala%20(living%20room)%2C%20we%20went%20to%20a%20silent%20disco.%20Even%20though%20it%20wasn't%20exactly%20the%20same%2C%20being%20together%20and%20dancing%20the%20night%20away%20in%20another%20country%20still%20felt%20like%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ea47273f-4c52-4f1c-9a5b-7fa7115b4918%5C%22%3EI%20can't%20wait%20to%20do%20it%20again%20this%20year%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222999%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20beach%20with%20blue%20water%20on%20a%20cloudy%20day.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6912564062a04500b3161bdd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222186%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20loved%20spending%20Thanksgiving%20on%20the%20beach.%3Cp%3ETaima%20Ramsey%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20got%20back%20home%2C%20I%20assumed%20this%20was%20a%20one-and-done%20deal.%20It%20was%20fun%2C%20but%20tradition%20is%20tradition%2C%20and%20we%20don't%20want%20to%20mess%20with%20that.%20Never%20in%20a%20million%20years%20did%20I%20think%20we'd%20ever%20do%20it%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20this%20year%2C%20during%20our%20annual%20Fourth%20of%20July%20weekend%20get-together%2C%20my%20aunt%20asked%20if%20we%20were%20going%20to%20Mexico%20again%20for%20Thanksgiving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20looked%20at%20each%20other%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20guess.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20now%2C%20here%20we%20are%2C%20getting%20ready%20to%20spend%20Thanksgiving%20for%20the%20second%20year%20in%20a%20row%20at%20an%20all-inclusive%20resort%20in%20Mexico.%20And%20I'm%20pretty%20sure%20this%20won't%20be%20the%20last%20%E2%80%94%20we're%20already%20looking%20at%20dates%20for%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcelebrated-thanksgiving-family-vacation-all-inclusive-resort-mexico-worth-it-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1763038021000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6903bdd1599d46a4ccc12c68%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcelebrated-thanksgiving-family-vacation-all-inclusive-resort-mexico-worth-it-2025-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Instead%20of%20hosting%20Thanksgiving%20dinner%2C%20my%20family%20traveled%20to%20an%20all-inclusive%20resort%20in%20Mexico.%20The%20unique%20celebration%20gave%20us%20more%20time%20to%20connect.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Taima%20Ramsey)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcelebrated-thanksgiving-family-vacation-all-inclusive-resort-mexico-worth-it-2025-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Epstein%20email%20says%20Andrew%20had%20photo%20taken%20with%20Virginia%20Giuffre%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1763037523000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk