0item%2C%20so%20anything%20that%20I%20made%20from%20it%20would%20be%20strictly%20profit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20back%20in%202005.%20Ogunsunlade%20had%20just%20started%20law%20school%20and%20was%20home%20for%20the%20holidays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20sold%20the%20perfume%20%26quot%3Bfairly%20quickly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20and%20then%20moved%20on%20to%20listing%20items%20from%20his%20closet.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20way%20too%20many%20clothes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20working%20his%20way%20through%20his%20closet%20items%2C%20the%20next%20step%20was%20to%20start%20shopping%20at%20discount%20stores%20for%20inventory.%20Gradually%2C%20over%20the%20last%20two%20decades%2C%20Ogunsunlade%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Febay-side-hustle-six-figures-lawyer-fashionably-legal-entrepreneurship-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuilt%20a%20six-figure%20side%20hustle%20reselling%20shoes%20and%20clothing%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20September%202024%20and%20September%202025%2C%20his%20company%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D206154102bfd2ecf051ccf2ba67d4a1e2f8e44089f199743dbd6d362cce08dcf%26postID%3D6913b81d28d6373f9430a8ae%26postSlug%3Dside-hustle-how-to-find-profitable-products-resell-on-ebay-2025-11%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.ebay.com%252Fstr%252Ffashionablylegal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFashionably%20Legal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20did%20%24120%2C000%20in%20sales%20on%20eBay%2C%20according%20to%20a%20screenshot%20of%20his%20seller%20hub%20dashboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20particular%20side%20hustle%2C%20the%20barrier%20to%20entry%20is%20extremely%20low%2C%20said%20Ogunsunlade%3A%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20startup%20cost.%26quot%3B%20You%20just%20have%20to%20be%20willing%20to%20invest%20time%2C%20he%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20more%20time%20that%20you%20put%20into%20researching%20items%20and%20sourcing%20items%2C%20the%20more%20items%20you%20can%20list.%20You%20see%20a%20direct%20return%20on%20the%20amount%20of%20effort%20that%20you%20put%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20eBay%20veteran%20shared%20where%20he%20shops%2C%20what%20he's%20looking%20for%2C%20and%20strategies%20he%20uses%20to%20ensure%20he'll%20turn%20a%20profit.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2214a93ec0-075c-429f-acfd-2b5d830d9438%5C%22%3ESource%20products%20from%20discount%20stores%20and%20sites%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Ogunsunlade%20first%20started%20reselling%20on%20eBay%2C%20he%20spent%20hours%20sifting%20through%20clothing%20racks%20for%20deals.%20He%20said%20he%20stopped%20by%20his%20two%20%26quot%3Bgo-to%26quot%3B%20stores%20%E2%80%94%20Neiman%20Marcus%20Last%20Call%20and%20Saks%20OFF%205th%20%E2%80%94%20almost%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20still%20spends%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20a%20week%20shopping%20in-store%2C%20but%20he's%20shifted%20to%20doing%20more%20%26quot%3Bonline%20arbitrage%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20saves%20him%20time%20and%20gas%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20just%20have%20the%20items%20sent%20directly%20to%20me%2C%20list%20them%20right%20away%2C%20and%20then%20get%20them%20shipped%20back%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ogunsunlade%2C%20who%20uses%20sites%20like%20YOOX%20and%20NET-A-PORTER%20to%20find%20great%20deals%20on%20luxury%20items.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20constantly%20on%20those%20websites%20looking%20for%20different%20sales%2C%20refreshing%20pages%2C%20seeing%20items%20coming%20in%20and%20out%20of%20stock.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESourcing%20items%20is%20time-consuming%20and%20can%20sometimes%20feel%20like%20a%20grind%2C%20he%20admitted.%20But%2C%20as%20someone%20who%20enjoys%20shopping%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bthrill%20of%20the%20hunt%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20never%20seemed%20like%20work%20to%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227cfd4562-c155-4436-be83-a1e9a53e4095%5C%22%3EPrice%20compare%20using%20the%20'sold%20items'%20section%20on%20eBay%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20succeed%20in%20any%20category%20on%20sites%20like%20eBay%2C%20you%20have%20to%20pay%20attention%20to%20two%20numbers%3A%20the%20price%20of%20the%20item%20you%20plan%20to%20buy%20and%20resell%2C%20and%20what%20comparable%20items%20have%20sold%20for%20on%20eBay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOgunsunlade%20advises%20browsing%20the%20%26quot%3Bsold%20items%26quot%3B%20section%20of%20your%20niche%20on%20eBay%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20is%20selling%20well%20and%20what%20isn't.%20You%20can%20also%20reference%20the%20sold%20items%20to%20ensure%20you'll%20turn%20a%20profit%2C%20rather%20than%20lose%20money%20on%20an%20item.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Yinka%20Ogunsunlade%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690e391521c3f142ebfc5509%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYinka%20Ogunsunlade%20is%20a%20full-time%20attorney%20by%20day%20and%20a%20six-figure%20entrepreneur%20by%20night.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Yinka%20Ogunsunlade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20first%20started%20on%20eBay%2C%20as%20he%20was%20shopping%20for%20inventory%2C%20he'd%20take%20photos%20of%20items%20along%20with%20their%20price%20tags.%20Then%2C%20he'd%20drive%20home%2C%20pull%20up%20eBay%20on%20his%20computer%20to%20look%20for%20what%20similar%20items%20sold%20for%2C%20and%20return%20to%20the%20department%20stores%20to%20buy%20the%20ones%20with%20the%20best%20profit%20margins.%20Now%2C%20thanks%20to%20smartphones%2C%20he%20can%20look%20up%20products%20on%20the%20spot%20and%20decide%20if%20the%20margins%20are%20strong%20enough%20to%20purchase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20essential%20to%20use%20the%20%26quot%3Bsold%20items%26quot%3B%20filter%20on%20eBay%2C%20he%20said%2C%20as%20there%20could%20be%20a%20big%20discrepancy%20between%20what%20something%20is%20listed%20for%20and%20what%20it%20sells%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223162389e-3a31-446c-a1ea-3a02c361339a%5C%22%3EPay%20attention%20to%20seasonal%20items%20and%20trends%2C%20but%20stick%20with%20what%20you%20know%20and%20love%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20been%20on%20eBay%20for%2020%20years%2C%20Ogunsunlade%20has%20started%20to%20notice%20patterns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20start%20of%20football%20season%2C%20for%20example%2C%20he%20stocks%20up%20on%20cleats%3A%20%26quot%3BOnce%20July%20and%20August%20roll%20around%2C%20I%20know%20there's%20a%20parent%20somewhere%20in%20America%20with%20a%20kid%20that%20needs%20some%20football%20cleats.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20he%20likes%20about%20his%20category%2C%20though%2C%20is%20that%20it's%20more%20resilient%20than%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody's%20always%20going%20to%20need%20a%20pair%20of%20running%20shoes%20or%20walking%20shoes%20or%20less%20formal%2C%20athletic%20wear%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Whereas%2C%20with%20a%20category%20like%20business%20attire%2C%20there%20can%20be%20more%20of%20an%20ebb%20and%20flow.%20%26quot%3BEspecially%20when%20COVID%20came%20around%2C%20people%20weren't%20going%20into%20the%20office%20and%20weren't%20even%20wearing%20business%20attire%2C%20so%20I%20saw%20a%20drop%20in%20people%20searching%20for%20neckties%20and%20formal%20wear%20online.%20I%20don't%20see%20those%20types%20of%20pronounced%20dips%20in%20the%20athletic%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20enjoys%20selling%20active%20wear%20the%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20definitely%20beneficial%20to%20sell%20something%20that%20you're%20passionate%20about%20%E2%80%94%20not%20to%20just%20sell%20it%20because%20you%20can%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20When%20selecting%20a%20category%20to%20specialize%20in%2C%20ask%20yourself%3A%20%26quot%3BDo%20you%20enjoy%20looking%20at%20this%20same%20style%2C%20this%20same%20type%20of%20item%20every%20day%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fside-hustle-how-to-find-profitable