n-musk-ai-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAshok%20Elluswamy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20spoke%20at%20an%20all-hands%20meeting%20for%20staff%20across%20Tesla's%20Autopilot%20and%20Optimus%20teams%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElluswamy%20said%202026%20will%20be%20a%20key%20test%20for%20the%20automaker%2C%20according%20to%20insiders.%20The%20executive%20told%20staffers%20that%20they%20should%20expect%20to%20work%20more%20intensely%20than%20ever%20to%20achieve%20the%20company's%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20person%20said%20the%20meeting%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Brallying%20cry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeaders%20from%20across%20the%20AI%20division%20spoke%20to%20staffers%20during%20the%20nearly%20two-hour%20meeting%2C%20insiders%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorkers%20were%20given%20aggressive%20timelines%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-optimus-humanoid-robot-training-elon-musk-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOptimus%20production%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20well%20as%20targets%20for%20Tesla's%20Robotaxi%20service.%20As%20Tesla%20races%20to%20launch%20Robotaxis%20across%20the%20nation%20and%20ramp%20up%20production%20of%20the%20company's%20humanoid%20robot%2C%20the%20two%20divisions%20are%20at%20the%20center%20of%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk's%20biggest%20bets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElluswamy%20and%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Tesla%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20during%20Tesla's%20earnings%20call%20in%20October%20that%20the%20company%20plans%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-robotaxi-deadline-hiring-testing-cities-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoperate%20its%20Robotaxi%20service%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20eight%20to%2010%20metropolitan%20areas%20by%20the%20end%20of%202025.%20He%20has%20also%20said%20the%20company%20aims%20to%20have%20more%20than%20a%20thousand%20ride-hailing%20vehicles%20on%20the%20road%20by%20the%20