0way%20to%20think%20about%20the%20per-user%20business%20is%20not%20just%20per%20user%2C%20it's%20per%20agent%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENadella's%20comments%20reflect%20a%20broader%20transformation%20underway%20across%20the%20industry%2C%20as%20AI%20systems%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-evolution-software-companies-develop-ai-agents-workforce-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebegin%20to%20use%20software%3C%2Fa%3E%20instead%20of%20merely%20being%20powered%20by%20it%20%E2%80%94%20and%20companies%20are%20rethinking%20how%20to%20charge%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsaas-ai-changing-how-software-companies-charge-customers-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20Alistair%20Barr%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20in%20April%20that%20software%20companies%20like%20ServiceNow%20are%20testing%20usage-based%20billing%20tied%20to%20AI%20workloads.%20As%20AI%20tools%20consume%20more%20compute%20with%20each%20query%20or%20inference%2C%20companies%20are%20finding%20it%20harder%20to%20sustain%20traditional%20flat%20%26quot%3Bper-seat%26quot%3B%20licenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20it%20goes%20beyond%20what%20we%20can%20credibly%20afford%2C%20we%20have%20to%20have%20some%20kind%20of%20meter%2C%26quot%3B%20Bill%20McDermott%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20ServiceNow%2C%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20enterprise%20world%2C%20the%20same%20shift%20is%20underway.%20Deloitte%20and%20EY%20launched%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeloitte-ey-launch-agentic-ai-platforms-big-four-competition2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eagentic%20AI%20platforms%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20March%2C%20where%20autonomous%20systems%20generate%20analyses%2C%20schedule%20work%2C%20and%20communicate%20with%20clients.%20Rather%20than%20charging%20based%20on%20the%20hours%20or%20human%20resources%20spent%20on%20a%20project%2C%20EY's%20global%20managing%20partner%20for%20growth%20and%20innovation%2C%20Raj%20Sharma%2C%20said%20these%20new%20models%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bservice-as-a-software%26quot%3B%20approach%2C%20where%20clients%20pay%20for%20outcomes%20delivered%20by%20AI%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENadella%20told%20the%20%26quot%3BDwarkesh%20Podcast%26quot%3B%20that%20under%20this%20vision%2C%20the%20company's%20services%2C%20such%20as%20its%20Microsoft%20365%20suite%2C%20would%20provide%20the%20core%20workspace%20for%20AI%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20stuff%20we%20built%20underneath%20M365%20still%20is%20going%20to%20be%20very%20relevant.%20You%20need%20some%20place%20to%20store%20it%2C%20some%20place%20to%20do%20archival%2C%20some%20place%20to%20do%20discovery%2C%20some%20place%20to%20manage%20all%20of%20these%20activities%2C%20even%20if%20you're%20an%20AI%20agent%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20infrastructure%20business%20is%20going%20to%20%26quot%3Bgrow%20faster%20than%20the%20number%20of%20users%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Microsoft%20introduced%20a%20pay-as-you-go%20pricing%20model%20for%20its%20AI%20agents.%20The%20metered%20system%20sits%20on%20top%20of%20a%20free%20Copilot%20chat%20experience%20for%20Microsoft%20365%20users%2C%20allowing%20companies%20to%20pay%20based%20on%20the%20amount%20of%20work%20their%20AI%20agents%20perform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20tech%20companies%20like%20Anthropic%20charge%20customers%20by%20usage%20%E2%80%94%20pricing%20its%20Claude%20models%20per%20million%20tokens%20processed.%20Google%20also%20applies%20a%20similar%20pay-as-you-go%20structure%20for%20its%20Gemini%20API.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-satya-nadella-software-pricing-ai-agent-copilot2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1763028368000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69156537e1a9cbb014de1bc8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-satya-nadella-software-pricing-ai-agent-copilot2025-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Satya%20Nadella%20says%20Microsoft%20is%20thinking%20about%20charging%20%26quot%3Bper%20agent%26quot%3B%20rather%20than%20%26quot%3Bper%20user%26quot%3B%20as%20more%20companies%20embrace%20agentic%20AI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cmlee%40insider.com%20(Lee%20Chong%20Ming)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-satya-nadella-software-pricing-ai-agent-copilot2025-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Unstable%20genius%3A%20DeepMind%20cracks%20a%20century-old%20physics%20mystery%20with%20AI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227245%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22High-speed%20photograph%20of%20secondary%20drop%20formation%20following%20the%20impact%20of%20a%20water%20droplet%20on%20water.%20The%20impact%20causes%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20pool%20to%20collapse%2C%20creating%20a%20rush%20of%20water%20inwards%20and%20upwards%20to%20form%20a%20column.%20Surface%20tension%20effects%20along%20the%20column%20cause%20a%20secondary%20drop%20to%20form.%20Shock%20waves%20radiate%20outwards%20as%20concentric%20circular%20ripples.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6914f03fabd5e944effa9c83%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224830%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20impact%20of%20a%20water%20droplet%20on%20water%3Cp%3EScience%20Photo%20Library%20via%20Reuters%20Connect%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EScientists%20struggle%20to%20predict%20how%20fluids%20behave.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGoogle's%20DeepMind%20lab%20recently%20made%20a%20major%20breakthrough%20in%20this%20area.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI'm%20not%20good%20at%20physics%2C%20so%20I%20asked%20my%20daughter%20Nora%20to%20explain%20why%20this%20is%20so%20important.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20over%20a%20century%2C%20mathematicians%20and%20physicists%20have%20wrestled%20with%20the%20chaotic%20nature%20of%20fluid%20movement%20%E2%80%94%20how%20air%20whirls%20around%20airplane%20wings%20or%20water%20churns%20in%20a%20pipe.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-apple-building-blocks-chatgpt-data-centers-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle%3C%2Fa%3E's%20DeepMind%20lab%20recently%20made%20a%20significant%20breakthrough%20in%20this%20field%2C%20utilizing%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20investors%20and%20others%20question%20whether%20AI%20will%20be%20worth%20the%20astronomical%20cost%2C%20it's%20reassuring%20to%20see%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeepmind-ceo-demis-hassabis-google-ai-future-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDeepMind%3C%2Fa%3E%20working%20on%20important%20stuff%20like%20this.%20This%20is%20an%20example%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fts-imagine-ai-roi-efficiency-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20producing%20something%20of%20real%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20reminder%2C%20DeepMind%20is%20a%20pioneering%20AI%20research%20lab%20that%20was%20acquired%20by%20Google%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20ago.%20It's%20led%20by%20Demis%20Hassabis%2C%20a%20math%20and%20gaming%20whizz%20who%20has%20risen%20quickly%20up%20Google's%20ranks%20as%20AI%20has%20become%20more%20powerful%20and%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228005%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Demis%20Hassabis%2C%20Google%20DeepMind%20CEO%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6915050889026fbb4d0d8994%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225339%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDemis%20Hassabis%2C%20Google%20DeepMind%20CEO%3Cp%3EDan%20Kitwood%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20a%20%26quot%3BG%26quot%3B%20grade%20in%20my%20first%20year%20of%20physics%20in%20high%20school%20(yes%2C%20you%20read%20that%20correctly).%20To%20explain%20the%20importance%20of%20DeepMind's%20recent%20discovery%2C%20I%20consulted%20my%20daughter%2C%20Nora%20Woolley%2C%20who's%20studying%20mechanical%20engineering%20and%20fluid%20dynamics!%20%E2%80%94%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20shared%20DeepMind's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdeepmind.google%2Fblog%2Fdiscovering-new-solutions-to-century-old-problems-in-fluid-dynamics%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblog%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fpdf%2F2509.14185%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresearch%20paper%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Nora%2C%20and%20she%20wrote%20back%20with%20her%20takeaways%20and%20some%20explanations%20for%20those%20of%20us%20who%20struggle%20with%20math%20and%20physics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20could%20have%20a%20big%20impact%20on%20fluid%20dynamics%20and%20physics%20as%20a%20whole%2C%26quot%3B%20Nora%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227c8b9af9-6cc0-4e6a-956f-8323657799ba%5C%22%3EConcentrate%20on%20this%20part%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOK%2C%20on%20to%20the%20details%2C%20with%20Nora's%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFluids%20are%20so%20unpredictable%20that%20the%20equations%20used%20to%20model%20their%20behavior%20are%20impossible%20to%20solve%20completely.%20To%20use%20these%20equations%2C%20physicists%20must%20make%20assumptions%20such%20as%20constant%20viscosity%20or%20a%20smooth%20change%20in%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIntroducing%20even%20simple%20scenarios%20can%20lead%20to%20%26quot%3Bblow-ups%26quot%3B%20where%20the%20equations%20predict%20extreme%20outcomes%20such%20as%20infinite%20pressure%20or%20an%20unbelievable%20surge%20in%20velocity.%20These%20are%20called%20singularities%2C%20and%20they%20represent%20the%20moments%20when%20math%20is%20no%20longer%20able%20to%20predict%20the%20physical%20behavior%20of%20fluids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESingularities%20can%20either%20be%20stable%20or%20unstable.%20Stable%20singularities%20are%20easier%20to%20find%2C%20while%20unstable%20ones%20are%20far%20harder%20to%20pin%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221783e623-217b-4c4d-9580-0c281ba337a1%5C%22%3EUnstable%20genius%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20machine%20learning%20and%20bespoke%2C%20physics-focused%20AI%20models%2C%20DeepMind%20researchers%20uncovered%20new%20families%20of%20unstable%20singularities%20across%20three%20distinct%20fluid-dynamics%20equations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20embedding%20the%20structure%20of%20the%20equations%20directly%20into%20these%20specialized%20AI%20models%20and%20optimizing%20them%20in%20stages%2C%20the%20team%20achieved%20near%20machine-level%20precision%2C%20enough%20for%20mathematicians%20to%20verify%20the%20results%20formally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20work%20provides%20a%20new%20playbook%20for%E2%80%A6%20tackling%20long-standing%20challenges%20in%20mathematical%20physics%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DeepMind%20researchers%20wrote%20in%20their%20research%20paper.%20An%20accompanying%20blog%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20breakthrough%20represents%20a%20new%20way%20of%20doing%20mathematical%20research.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2256ce8897-25b8-4723-9a53-edf5cf62dcd3%5C%22%3EWhy%20it%20matters%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20discovery%20of%20these%20new%20unstable%20singularities%20may%20help%20scientists%20better%20understand%20how%20turbulence%2C%20the%20unpredictable%20and%20energy-draining%20behavior%20of%20fluids%2C%20happens%20in%20nature%20and%20engineering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20unlocks%20a%20deeper%20understanding%20of%20areas%20such%20as%20aircraft%20drag%2C%20weather%20systems%2C%20blood%20flow%2C%20and%20energy%20distribution.%20Who%20knows%2C%20these%20discoveries%20might%20make%20future%20flights%20less%20bumpy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENora%20said%20the%20breakthroughs%20may%20help%20monitor%20%26quot%3Bturbidity%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20state%20where%20fluids%20are%20governed%20by%20momentum%20rather%20than%20physical%20properties%2C%20making%20it%20hard%20to%20predict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20the%20software%20we%20use%20to%20monitor%20turbidity%20assumes%20that%20these%20equations%20are%20fully%20accurate%20across%20all%20values%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20DeepMind%20has%20discovered%20new%20unstable%20singularities%2C%20scientists%20may%20be%20able%20to%20monitor%20turbid%20flows%20better%2C%20%26quot%3BBecause%20we%20have%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20the%20ranges%20where%20these%20equations%20are%20valid%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20AI%20curing%20cancer%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20lot%20better%20than%20the%20generative%20AI%20slop%20currently%20infecting%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESign%20up%20for%20BI's%20Tech%20Memo%20newsletter%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Ftech-memo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Reach%20out%20to%20me%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabarr%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabarr%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-deepmind-cracks-century-old-physics-mystery-ai-fluid-dynamics-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1763028002000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6914f060abd5e944effa9c8b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-deepmind-cracks-century-old-physics-mystery-ai-fluid-dynamics-2025-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Scientists%20struggle%20with%20the%20physics%20of%20fluids.%20A%20recent%20Google%20breakthrough%20could%20support%20better%2